name: Peronne Goguillon
description:
Peronne was burned to death on the 29th of May, 1679, as an alleged French witch 

She and other women accused with her are regarded as the last women to have been burned at the stake for witchcraft in France

One of a series working with AI to give face to women executed as witches; these form part of a broader collection of Horror Portraits at www.darkart.studio

#HENHalloween

Can be used as #PFP and #wallpaper

PNG 4800 x 4800
